metadata.name: Gorgoz The Unrepentant
metadata.description:
Gorgoz The Unrepentant (portrayed by Krassin Wratch Jr.) was a character who appeared in Season 3 of 'Legends of The Golden Child'.

Gorgoz was the Chief Psychopomp of The Wizard's Bend Necromancy Guild.

3000x4500 Pixels.
Made in Collaboration with Midjourney.
